    &lt;dcc:dataBase64&gt;BASE64_PDF_BYTES_HERE==&lt;/dcc:dataBase64&gt;
  &lt;/dcc:file&gt;
&lt;/drmd:description&gt;
</code></pre> <p>Schematron Rule: RMC-011</p> <p>Reference Material Certificates MUST include a description for each material (ISO 33401:2024, §5.3.2). Severity: Error. This rule does not apply to <code>productInformationSheet</code> documents, but a description is still recommended (PIS-005, Severity: Warning).</p>

Property Value Path <code>.../drmd:material/drmd:materialClass</code> Type <code>drmd:materialClassType</code> Cardinality Optional, repeatable <code>[0..∞]</code> <p>Purpose: A classification entry that ties the material to a classification scheme and a class identifier within that scheme.</p> <pre><code>graph LR
    MC["materialClass"] --&gt; REF["reference&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i&gt;Required&lt;/i&gt;"]
    MC --&gt; CID["classID&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i&gt;Required&lt;/i&gt;"]
