  &lt;/dcc:content&gt;
&lt;/drmd:subcontractors&gt;
</code></pre>

Cardinality Optional (<code>[0..1]</code>) <p>Legal disclaimers, liability limitations, permitted use, and rights. Keep text clear and jurisdiction-appropriate.</p> <pre><code>&lt;drmd:legalNotice&gt;
  &lt;dcc:content lang="en"&gt;
    The producer's liability is limited to replacement of the material. Use is subject to
